{%- comment -%}
  Accepted payment icons — grayscale row via Shopify's own
  `payment_type_svg_tag` filter (spec: "payment icons in grayscale"/
  "outline style" — no icon set to maintain, always matches whatever the
  merchant actually has enabled in Settings → Payments). Extracted from
  the cart page (Milestone 8) once the footer (Milestone 11) needed the
  exact same row.

  Accepts: class (optional): extra class on each icon, for size overrides.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if shop.enabled_payment_types.size > 0 -%}
  <div class="payment-icons">
    {%- for type in shop.enabled_payment_types -%}
      {{ type | payment_type_svg_tag: class: 'payment-icons__icon ' | append: class }}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
{%- endif -%}
